.TH "rio_get_host_deviceid_lock" 9 "rio_get_host_deviceid_lock" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
rio_get_host_deviceid_lock \- Reads the Host Device ID Lock CSR on a device
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "u16" rio_get_host_deviceid_lock
.BI "(struct rio_mport *port "  ","
.BI "u8 hopcount "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "port" 12
Master port to send transaction
.IP "hopcount" 12
Number of hops to the device
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Used during enumeration to read the Host Device ID Lock CSR on a
RIO device. Returns the value of the lock register.
